   https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Bug/Display.html?id=92676
 - Impl/Default.pm: fix indirect call of autoflush on STDOUT
 - Impl/Parser.pm: perl tidy
 - Impl/Parser.pm: removed call to $r->events, not used

